snippet.title: Diana and Roma Help mom and decorate the Christmas tree
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma remember that Christmas is coming soon. They really want to decorate the Christmas tree. Diana and Roma help their mother: they wash the dishes, clean the house, wash clothes and more. Mom gives the children money to buy Christmas toys. Diana and Roma helped their mother great and decorated the Christmas tree!
Thanks for watching!
